### The idea
1. Use one hashmap `nodeHash` to store information between key:node
2. Use another hashmap `freqHash` to store information between freq:dll (doublylinkedlist)
3. Use Doublylinkedlist to store a LRU for a given freq
4. I use dummy head&tail for easier implementation
