Step 2. You need another Map to maintain frequency count. make sure to remove from the map when ejecting an element from the LinkedHashMap

Step 3. have a HashSet to capture equal frequency entries.

The rest is easy 

	class LFUCache {
		int capacity;
		Map<Integer, Integer> countMap;
		Map<Integer, Integer> map;
